data.description: Welcome to this oversized Single Family Home that lives like a Multifamily, in an ideal location.  This home is big enough to accommodate your entire family, plus an extra 2 bedrooms and 1 full bathroom in the basement to fit all needs, with exterior access.  Close to Lynn Beach, Commuter Rail, NSCC, Central Square and walking distance to restaurants and wine shops, this home is centrally located to get you into the city quickly or a quick jog down the beach.  72 Newhall has exquisite woodwork that has been cared for throughout the years and 3 fireplaces to keep your loved ones warm during these cold winter days.  Come check out this gorgeous Victorian and with a few special touches make it yours today!
